and everyone who knows where they are.</font>

197
00:18:10,924 --> 00:18:12,925
<font color="#FFFFFF">And no fuckin' exceptions!</font>

198
00:18:26,396 --> 00:18:27,480
<font color="#FFFFFF">Show me.</font>

199
00:18:27,981 --> 00:18:31,692
<font color="#FFFFFF">We backtracked 47 minutes.
Clearly anticipated the CCTV:</font>

200
00:18:31,776 --> 00:18:34,320
