<font color="#FFFFFF">I'll call the moment I have something.</font>

796
01:14:06,033 --> 01:14:07,451
<font color="#FFFFFF">It better be soon,</font>

797
01:14:07,534 --> 01:14:10,295
<font color="#FFFFFF">or you'll feel a backlash the likes
