808
01:14:39,188 --> 01:14:40,771
<font color="#FFFFFF">Belfast will erupt.</font>

809
01:14:40,855 --> 01:14:43,317
<font color="#FFFFFF">You'll give the bombers
exactly what they want.</font>

810
01:14:43,399 --> 01:14:46,234
