848
01:17:28,921 --> 01:17:30,465
<font color="#FFFFFF">Are you sure now?</font>

849
01:17:30,631 --> 01:17:31,631
<font color="#FFFFFF">Quite.</font>

850
01:17:32,675 --> 01:17:36,095
<font color="#FFFFFF">We've ID'd the Knightsbridge bomber
