892
01:19:42,957 --> 01:19:45,002
<font color="#FFFFFF">You're a disgrace to the cause.</font>

893
01:19:47,752 --> 01:19:49,046
<font color="#FFFFFF">Four men and a woman.</font>

894
01:19:53,634 --> 01:19:54,969
<font color="#FFFFFF">Maggie Dunn?</font>

