01:19:55,176 --> 01:19:58,137
<font color="#FFFFFF">Aye. You call her that.</font>

896
01:19:59,014 --> 01:20:01,265
<font color="#FFFFFF">Sara Mackay's her real name.</font>

897
01:20:04,101 --> 01:20:05,519
<font color="#FFFFFF">She works for you?</font>

898
01:20:06,395 --> 01:20:07,938
<font color="#FFFFFF">Bloody right.</font>

899
01:20:08,021 --> 01:20:09,355
<font color="#FFFFFF">Checks and balances.</font>

900
01:20:12,984 --> 01:20:18,155
<font color="#FFFFFF">An insurance policy,
in case you lose your nerve,</font>

901
01:20:18,238 --> 01:20:22,076
