01:20:50,935 --> 01:20:52,978
<font color="#FFFFFF">who they ID'd as the Knightsbridge bomber.</font>

911
01:20:53,229 --> 01:20:55,980
<font color="#FFFFFF">And thanks to your GPS phone,
